msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/date"
msgid "December 20th, 1944 · Samree, Ardennes, Belgium"
msgstr "20 de diciembre, 1944 - Samree, Ardenas, Bélgica"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/doctrine_allround"
msgid "Doctrine: All-Round"
msgstr "Doctrina: Completa"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/doctrine_defensive"
msgid "Doctrine: Defensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: Defensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/doctrine_irregular"
msgid "Doctrine: Irregular"
msgstr "Doctrina: Irregular"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/doctrine_offensive"
msgid "Doctrine: Offensive"
msgstr "Doctrina: Ofensiva"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/mission_option_select1"
msgid "Select your Doctrine for the mission:"
msgstr "Seleccione su Estrategia para la misión:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/name"
msgid "Wacht Am Rhein"
msgstr "Wacht Am Rhein"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/name_big"
msgid "Wacht Am Rhein"
msgstr "Wacht Am Rhein"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/01"
msgid ""
"Welcome to the Ardennes, Soldaten! We aim to strike a devastating blow to "
"the Allies, but in running around to find an intact bridge we have almost "
"run out of fuel."
msgstr ""
"¡Bienvenidos a las Ardenas, Soldaten! Nuestro objetivo es asestar un golpe "
"devastador a los Aliados, pero dando vueltas para encontrar un puente "
"intacto casi nos hemos quedado sin combustible."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/02"
msgid ""
"Today you are tasked with seizing the depot at Samrée. From there, we will "
"secure the neighboring town of Dochamps."
msgstr ""
"Hoy tienen la tarea de tomar el depósito de Samrée. Desde allí, aseguraremos "
"la ciudad vecina de Dochamps."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/03"
msgid ""
"Your first objective is to secure the crossroads up ahead, so our armored "
"column can be deployed. After that, lead our forces into Samrée!"
msgstr ""
"Tu primer objetivo es asegurar la encrucijada, para que nuestra columna "
"blindada pueda desplegarse. Después de eso, ¡lidera nuestras fuerzas hacia "
"Samrée!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/04"
msgid ""
"Well done, now our armor is here to lead the way. The Americans have some "
"serious firepower, so advance cautiously."
msgstr ""
"Bien hecho, ahora nuestro blindado está aquí para liderar el camino. Los "
"americanos tienen una gran potencia de fuego, así que avancen con cautela."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/05"
msgid ""
"The Americans have an artillery battery nearby which has been bothering us "
"all day. There must be a radio station at Samrée transmitting our "
"coordinates to the artillery. Silence that radioman if you want the "
"bombardment to stop!"
msgstr ""
"Los americanos tienen una batería de artillería cerca que nos ha estado "
"molestando todo el día. Debe haber una estación de radio en Samrée "
"transmitiendo nuestras coordenadas a la artillería. ¡Silencien a ese "
"controlador de radio si quieren que cese el bombardeo!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/06"
msgid "Enemy artillery is bombarding us! Move your troops out of there!"
msgstr "¡La artillería enemiga nos está bombardeando! ¡Saca tus tropas de ahí!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/07"
msgid ""
"Very good, the American radio operator is no more. The enemy artillery has "
"been silenced."
msgstr ""
"Muy bien, el operador de radio americano ya no está. La artillería enemiga "
"ha sido silenciada."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/08"
msgid ""
"As you make your way to Samrée, make sure to protect the fuel supplies if "
"you find any. We need it!"
msgstr ""
"Mientras te diriges a Samrée, asegúrate de proteger los suministros de "
"combustible si encuentras alguno. ¡Los necesitamos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/09"
msgid "Excellent job Soldaten! Samrée is ours."
msgstr "¡Excelente trabajo Soldaten! Samrée es nuestro."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/10"
msgid ""
"Next we are tasked with heading north and driving the Americans out of "
"Dochamps. We should expect enemy counterattacks from that direction, take a "
"defensive stance for the time being!"
msgstr ""
"Nuestra próxima tarea es dirigirnos al norte y expulsar a los americanos de "
"Dochamps. Debemos estar atentos a los contraataques enemigos desde esa "
"dirección, ¡adopta una posición defensiva por el momento!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/11"
msgid ""
"We can get further reinforcements, but our columns are pinned down by the "
"American artillery. You must eliminate the artillery battery on the hill, "
"the one that gave us a hard time earlier."
msgstr ""
"Podemos conseguir más refuerzos, pero nuestras columnas están siendo "
"inmovilizadas por la artillería americana. Debéis eliminar la batería de "
"artillería de la colina, la que nos lo puso difícil antes."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/12"
msgid ""
"I would advise you to first fend off any enemy counterattacks, and then "
"storm the hill. Do that and receive reinforcements to attack Dochamps with "
"additional troops."
msgstr ""
"Te aconsejo que primero rechaces cualquier contraataque enemigo y luego "
"asaltes la colina. Hazlo y recibe a los refuerzos para atacar Dochamps con "
"tropas adicionales."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/13"
msgid ""
"Excellent work Soldaten! The M7 Priests on the hill are all silenced. Our "
"reinforcements are getting themselves sorted and should be here any minute "
"now."
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo Soldaten! Los M7 Priests de la colina han sido "
"silenciados. Nuestros refuerzos se las están arreglando para llegar hasta "
"aquí en cualquier momento."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/14"
msgid ""
"Excellent work Soldaten! Dochamps is ours, and this is a key step in our "
"winter offensive. I can assure you, Iron crosses will be requested for "
"today's accomplishments!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo Soldaten! Dochamps es nuestro, este es un paso clave en "
"nuestra ofensiva de invierno. ¡Les aseguro que obtendrán cruces de hierro "
"por los logros de hoy!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/15"
msgid ""
"Our reinforcements are here! Now that the American counter-battery threat is "
"eliminated, you get access to long range artillery!"
msgstr ""
"¡Nuestros refuerzos están aquí! Ahora que la amenaza de contra-batería "
"americana ha sido eliminada, ¡tienes acceso a artillería de largo alcance!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/90mm"
msgid ""
"The enemy has very nasty 90mm AA guns which are a threat even to our "
"heaviest of Panzers. Advance cautiously, and watch out for large circular "
"fortifications that could house such guns. We cannot afford to lose armor "
"today!"
msgstr ""
"El enemigo tiene unos cañones AA de 90 mm muy desagradables que son una "
"amenaza incluso para nuestros Panzer más pesados. Avanzad con cautela y "
"tened cuidado con las grandes fortificaciones circulares que son las que "
"pueden albergar este tipo de cañones. ¡No podemos permitirnos perder "
"blindados hoy!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/reinf1"
msgid "Enemy counterattack approaching Samrée!"
msgstr "¡Contraataque enemigo acercándose a Samrée!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/narrator/reinf2"
msgid ""
"A large enemy column is approaching from Dochamps towards Samrée! Get ready "
"to hold them back!"
msgstr ""
"¡Una gran columna enemiga se acerca desde Dochamps hacia Samrée! ¡Prepárense "
"para contenerlos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"The road to Antwerp is open! No matter what happens after this, your "
"achievement will not be forgotten. General von Waldenburg is very happy with "
"your work! The allies will not be able to stop us now that we have an "
"abundance of fuel. Good work, commander!"
msgstr ""
"¡El camino hacia Amberes está abierto! No importa lo que pase después de "
"esto, su logro no será olvidado. ¡El General von Waldenburg está muy "
"contento con su trabajo! Los aliados no podrán detenernos ahora que nos "
"sobra combustible. ¡Buen trabajo, comandante!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/outro_failed"
msgid ""
"Well, that didn’t work out as General von Waldenburg planned - and that’s an "
"understatement, to say the least. We’re stuck here, with little chance of "
"achieving any of the goals that were set for your unit. You will have to try "
"again, using different tactics!\n"
msgstr ""
"Bueno, esto no ha funcionado como el General von Waldenburg planeó - y eso "
"es un eufemismo, por no decir que ha sido un desastre. Estamos atrapados "
"aquí, con pocas posibilidades de lograr cualquiera de los objetivos que se "
"establecieron para su unidad. Tendrás que intentarlo de nuevo, ¡usando "
"tácticas diferentes!\n"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/place"
msgid "116th Panzer Division"
msgstr "116ª División Panzer"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/reinf_arty"
msgid "Artillery strike"
msgstr "Ataque de artillería"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/story"
msgid " December 20th, 1944. Just four days ago, the Germans have sprung a big surprise by mounting a massive offensive in the Ardennes. In a sudden lunge toward the town of Antwerp, German armored columns push west, covered by bad weather. For a few days, the offensive moves with relative ease. But then, the 116th Panzer Division reaches Samrée.\n\n In this mission, you will lead the spearhead of the 116th Panzer Division. The disposition of enemy units is unknown. Our scouts report that the road ahead is blocked; so it seems the Americans know that Samrée is important to us. You have orders to eliminate the roadblock with limited resources. Remember; if you want to get our offensive going again, you will have to take control of Samrée quickly.\n\nGood luck!"
msgstr ""
"20 de diciembre, 1944.\n"
"\n"
"Hace sólo cuatro días, los alemanes han dado una gran sorpresa\n"
"\n"
"montando una ofensiva masiva en las Ardenas.\n"
"\n"
"En una arremetida repentina hacia la ciudad de Amberes,\n"
"\n"
"columnas blindadas alemanas avanzan hacia el oeste, cubiertas por el mal "
"tiempo.\n"
"\n"
"Durante unos días, la ofensiva avanza con relativa facilidad.\n"
"\n"
"Pero entonces, la 116ª División Panzer alcanza Samrée.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"En esta misión, usted dirigirá\n"
"\n"
"la punta de lanza de la 116ª División Panzer.\n"
"\n"
"Se desconoce la disposición de las unidades enemigas.\n"
"\n"
"Nuestros exploradores informan que la carretera está bloqueada;\n"
"\n"
"así que parece que los americanos saben que Samrée es importante para "
"nosotros.\n"
"\n"
"Tiene órdenes de eliminar el bloqueo de la carretera con recursos\n"
"\n"
"limitados.\n"
"\n"
"Recuerda; si quieres que nuestra ofensiva vuelva a funcionar,\n"
"\n"
"tendrás que tomar el control de Samrée rápidamente.\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"\n"
"¡Buena suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/task1"
msgid ""
"Eliminate the Americans at the crossroads for the main column to arrive."
msgstr ""
"Eliminar a los americanos en el cruce para que pueda llegar la columna "
"principal."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/task2"
msgid "Seize the town of Samrée and resupply fuel"
msgstr "Tomar la ciudad de Samrée y reponer combustible"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/task3"
msgid ""
"Take out the enemy artillery battery at the hill and acquire further "
"reinforcements"
msgstr ""
"Eliminar la batería de artillería enemiga de la colina y conseguir más "
"refuerzos"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/task4"
msgid "Drive the enemy off the town of Dochamps."
msgstr "Expulsar al enemigo de la ciudad de Dochamps."

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/timer1"
msgid "Time until American counterattack at Samrée:"
msgstr "Tiempo hasta el contraataque americano en Samrée:"

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger-west/1944_12_samree/timer2"
msgid "Time until next counterattack:"
msgstr "Tiempo hasta el próximo contraataque:"
